#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1685
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"SHIPVORE_RAM_OWN_OUTCOME_BAD_CREW\"]/choice[13]/event/removeCrew/text"
